#: ../../src/config/proxying.rst:89
msgid ""
"The proxy service is basic. If the request is not identified by the "
"``DESTINATION``, or the remainder of the ``PATH`` specification is "
"incomplete, the original request URL is interpreted as if the ``PREFIX`` "
"component of that URL does not exist."
msgstr ""

#: ../../src/config/proxying.rst:94
msgid ""
"For example, requesting ``http://couchdb:5984/_intranet/media`` when "
"``/media`` on the proxy destination does not exist, will cause the request "
"URL to be interpreted as ``http://couchdb:5984/media``. Care should be taken"
" to ensure that both requested URLs and destination URLs are able to cope."
msgstr ""
